metadata.name: LAC Presents: "Greetings from Miami" by: Art Fitzgerald
metadata.description: Greeting from Miami. A unique collection presented by the LAC (Lost Artist Collective) with a take on simply postcards. We asked a group of exclusive artists to design and make postcards to commemorate Art Basel Miami. Proceeds will fund a mural to be created in Miami by exclusive artists, and other activities there. See you in Miami!
